---
layout: html.njk
main_url: lipops.jirm.eu
---

<div class="l_center">

  <header class="l_box">
    <div class="l_cluster l_box" style="--l_cluster__jc:space-around;">

      <a href="https://hackstub.eu">
        <div class="l_frame" style="block-size: var(--logo-size); --l_frame__fit:contain;">
          <img src="/logo/hackstub_psyke_sml.jpg">
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://arn-fai.net">
        <div class="l_frame" style="block-size: var(--logo-size); --l_frame__fit:contain;">
          <img src="/logo/arn_simple.svg">
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://lafab.org/">
        <div class="l_frame" style="block-size: var(--logo-size); --l_frame__fit:contain;">
          <img src="/logo/lafab.svg">
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
    <hr>
  </header>


  <article class="l_flow l_box">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </article>


  <footer class="l_box l_flow">
    <hr>

    <div class="l_repel" style="--l_repel__wrap : nowrap">
      <div class="l_flow">
        <p><strong>Document à jour disponible sur <a href="http://{{ main_url }}">{{ main_url }}</a></strong></p>
        <small>LiPOPS - Libre & Populaire à Strasbourg : organisation coordonnées d'ateliers d'éducation populaire sur
          la libération numérique.
          Organisé par les associations
          <a href="https://lafab.org">La Fabrique</a>,
          <a href="https://arn-fai.net">Alsace Réseau Neutre</a> et
          <a href="https://hackstub.eu">Hackstub</a>
          Mise à jour le {{page.date | dateFull}}. 
          </small>
      </div>
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0;">{% qrcode "http://"+main_url, 100, "QR code", "qrcode" %}</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>